Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:01.540
Endi studiyada,

00:00:01.540 --> 00:00:06.580
men oldingi yo‘riqnomada berilgan
kod parchasi bilan faoliyatning asosiy 

00:00:06.580 --> 00:00:10.110
tartibini raqamlar toifasidagi 
matn ko‘rinishini almashtirish uchun o‘zgartirdim.

00:00:10.110 --> 00:00:14.490
Shunday qilib, men qora rangli "textColor" dan
boshqa fon uchun ranglarni ham qo‘shdim.

00:00:14.490 --> 00:00:17.590
Endi men ilovani qurilmamga o‘rnataman va
uning ko‘rinishi qanday ekanligini ko‘raman.

00:00:17.590 --> 00:00:19.820
Shunday qilib, yangi versiya ishlamoqda.

00:00:19.820 --> 00:00:23.540
Xo‘sh, raqamlarning matn 
ko‘rinishida endi rangli fon yo‘q.

00:00:23.540 --> 00:00:26.660
Bu kutilgan natija, chunki,
men fon rangini o‘zgartirdim.

00:00:26.660 --> 00:00:29.160
Shunday qilib, endi fon butun 
faoliyat singari 

00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:31.130
bir xil rangda.

00:00:31.130 --> 00:00:32.890
Xo‘sh, test savolining javobiga to‘xtaladigan bo‘lsak,

00:00:32.890 --> 00:00:35.190
biz raqamlar faoliyatini 
bosganimizda nimani kuzatamiz?

00:00:35.190 --> 00:00:36.740
Keling, uning ko‘rinishi qanday bo‘lishini ko‘raylik.

00:00:36.740 --> 00:00:38.580
Endi men raqamlar faoliyatini bosaman. 

00:00:38.580 --> 00:00:39.830
Men uni bo‘shatganimda

00:00:39.830 --> 00:00:43.520
barmog‘im bilan pastga tusha boshlaganimda,
yoqimli kulrang doira animatsiyasini ko‘rishim mumkin.

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:46.440
Bo‘shatilganidan so‘ng, 
tugmacha bosganimizdan keyin

00:00:46.440 --> 00:00:48.180
raqamlar faoliyati ochiladi.

00:00:48.180 --> 00:00:51.050
Endi esa orqaga qayting va buni yana 
bir marta ishga tushiring, chunki bu juda tez sodir bo‘ladi.

00:00:51.050 --> 00:00:55.848
Agar buni ushlay olsangiz, uni ko‘rishingiz mumkin.
